1. Decide which business to order from 
2. Decide which type of pizza to order
3. Select pizza company to order from
4. Place order thru pizza hut
5a. IF paying online for delivery
    - Make purchase of pizza online
    - Wait for delivery
    - Tip the driver
5b. IF paying online for pickup
    - Make purchase of pizza online
    - Allow 30-45 minutes to Pickup pizza from pizza Hut